title: "Baesys"
type: "Frontend"
year: "2025"
description: "A modern business system with streamlined operations and elegant interface design."
tags: ["React", "TypeScript", "Tailwind"]
image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757148-5c350d0d3c56?w=1200&h=760&fit=crop&auto=format"
